Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.01,0:00:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.15,0:00:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好 初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.95,0:00:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是搬到隔壁的新邻居
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以来跟你打声招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.01,0:00:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.08,0:00:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是一点小东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.01,0:00:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你客气了 谢谢 不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.68,0:00:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是您的女儿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.61,0:00:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错 叫做萤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.15,0:00:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.01,0:00:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小萤初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我家也有差不多年纪的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然他很内向 但下次一定让他出来欢迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.95,0:00:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我家发生了许多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.75,0:00:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我跟我女儿住而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.28,0:01:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还好有相同年龄的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.15,0:01:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱哦 小萤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.95,0:01:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乃木萤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.35,0:01:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（搬到隔壁的 无防备巨乳美少女）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.68,0:01:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（与家里蹲（我）的欲望）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.81,0:01:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,（乃木萤）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大地 小萤来家里玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打招呼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.75,0:02:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.21,0:02:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.95,0:02:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萤的父亲在做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不常回来 晚上也一个人在公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想说萤也会寂寞 就请她来家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给你冰淇淋 要吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.75,0:02:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈今天要去练芭蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.88,0:02:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小萤交给你照顾喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小萤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.21,0:02:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冰滇淋融化了哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.41,0:02:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面纸给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,该不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.48,0:03:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小萤没有穿内衣吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.08,0:03:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还巨乳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.48,0:03:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明知道家里有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.61,0:03:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么还这应没戒心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.95,0:03:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这该不会是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那个意思吧 ,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.61,0:04:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小萤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.75,0:04:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都黏答答的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.75,0:04:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去浴室冲一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.28,0:04:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,骗人的吧 这孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难不成真的有那个意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.55,0:04:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浴室在这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.81,0:04:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.28,0:05:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到这场景会发生在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.08,0:05:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身体超级性感的钦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.21,0:05:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不去冲水吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.95,0:05:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.15,0:05:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.21,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我帮你冲水呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.81,0:05:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我会帮你冲干净的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先进去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要冲罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.95,0:06:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另一边也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她都不会抵抗的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且还有感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.41,0:08:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小萤换好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.15,0:08:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小萤好可爱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.41,0:09:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好适合你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.68,0:09:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这套服装是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.41,0:09:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个作品的女王的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.01,0:09:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就知道你会很适合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.48,0:09:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.75,0:09:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也让我看看背后吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.35,0:09:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太棒了 对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.61,0:09:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再转过来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.01,0:09:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我从平时就最爱角色扮演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.15,0:09:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小萤真的太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.68,0:10:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再让识仔细看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.15,0:10:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.15,0:10:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的好棒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.68,0:10:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好适合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.08,0:10:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.88,0:11:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.81,0:11:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有这么适合角色扮演的美少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.21,0:11:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还想模更多地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.88,0:11:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我确认一下好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小萤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.28,0:12:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.68,0:12:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亲你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想亲嘴唇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.95,0:13:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.15,0:14:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你都直直盯着我看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.41,0:14:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想不想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.48,0:14:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摸下我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.55,0:15:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手借我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.95,0:15:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样握着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.75,0:15:12.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后动动看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.01,0:15:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看看自己在摸什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.15,0:15:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实也不知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.21,0:15:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那要不要靠近一点看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.41,0:16:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就直接蹲下来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.08,0:16:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手再握上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.81,0:16:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看着正握着的地方．
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.81,0:16:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.55,0:16:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以看看我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.55,0:17:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是在摸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.55,0:17:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放进嘴巴里看看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那把嘴巴张开吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脸可以再靠近一点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.68,0:17:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就这样 嘴巴能前后动吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.08,0:18:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.88,0:18:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手放开一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.41,0:18:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.35,0:18:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像在作梦 竟然有女生帮忙口交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.95,0:19:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难得这么棒的角色扮演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.75,0:19:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稍微
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过来这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.35,0:20:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直都想这样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.68,0:20:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.28,0:20:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小莹能懂吗 这样超舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.55,0:21:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.41,0:22:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用你的嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.75,0:22:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,含住我的肉棒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.15,0:22:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.75,0:23:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也用手握着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.95,0:23:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后舌尖舔着上面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.61,0:24:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没想到舌头能这么舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.75,0:24:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再含进嘴巴里面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.88,0:24:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.95,0:25:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.55,0:25:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:35.21,0:25:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又弄脏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.81,0:25:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再来冲一次水吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.68,0:26:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:17.61,0:26:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好冷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.81,0:26:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.75,0:26:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.41,0:26:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你穿这个看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.21,0:26:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.35,0:27:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超适合你的哎 小萤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:04.68,0:27:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是某个作品的角色的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:05.08,0:27:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.15,0:27:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可爱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:10.41,0:27:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,超级可爱的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:14.28,0:27:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我看看后面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:21.61,0:27:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这孩子是怎样 怎么这么听话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.35,0:27:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且这个屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:30.01,0:27:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女孩子的屁股威觉好软啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.68,0:27:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:39.48,0:27:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在衣服底下一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:44.81,0:29:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小萤舒服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:53.35,0:29:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:32.01,0:30:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小萤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:35.88,0:30:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.88,0:30:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以贴着你的屁股吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:44.01,0:30:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以吗
